dcterms:description: The MIMIC-III database consists of de-identified information about patients admitted to critical care units between 2001 and 2012. It encompasses an array of data types such as diagnostic codes, survival rates, and more.
dcterms:title: MIMIC-III

dcterms:description: The MIMIC-III benchmark datasets provide public benchmarks for four different clinical tasks: mortality prediction, detection of physiologic decompensation, forecasting length of stay, and phenotyping.
dcterms:title: MIMIC-III benchmark datasets
